show.description: Ordinary girl Annie crosses paths with Leon, the werewolf leader, bound by a prophecy from the Moon Goddess. But with memories erased and secrets hidden, Leon mistakes her sister for his fated mate. As boss and subordinate, they slowly fall in love. When memories return, truths surface, and Annie awakens with the Moon Goddess’s mysterious powers. How will her true identity reshape their fate—and can their love survive the unknown?
